data.description: Beautiful Custom Home has been remodel and is on a Wide spacious 1 acre lot. Large, very spacious Solid Built Home. Updates Galore.... Kitchen was remodeled in '23 and is absolutely gorgeous, updates include new cabinetry, granite countertops, microwave, large new sink. Enjoy the cool evenings with an electric fireplace in the family room. There is NO CARPET in this home. Beautiful crown molding in all the main living part of the home. Master Bath has a walk in separate shower, Jacuzzi style jet tub, large vanity area with separate bathroom for your own privacy, tile floors and a large walk in closet. Home has a heated and cooled Florida room with 288 square feet that is not included in the square footage, total square feet is 2,052.  More updates feature: New Roof '23, hall bath remodeled '18, Hurricane impact windows '18, new flooring, freshly painted interior '23, new gutters '22, new garage door '22, rainsoft water softener '18, new driveway '23. New patio '23. Florida room makes for the most relaxing atmosphere and the perfect room for family gatherings or entertainment area. Back yard is fenced Chain length. Feels like you're in the country when you're actually just minutes from the heart of Pace. Large over size 2.5 garage sitting on a beautiful 1 acre setting. Yard maintenance will be a breeze with a separate well for the lawn Sprinkler system. Additional faucets added for the back yard. Has 50 amp hook up for an RV with room to park up to 45 foot motor home. Double gate access to back of property. Bring your toys.  Plenty room for them all. Nice side workshop.  Brick custom home with too many updates to name them all. The seller has a Choice Home Warranty that is good until 10/21/27 that will transfer to new owners. This offers great peace of mind.
